name: hanes_socks
description: Give your feet the comfort they deserve with these Hanes Men's Cushion Crew Socks, 6 Pairs. They feature a reinforced heel and toe for enhanced durability. The extra support provided by the cushioned sole helps reduce the impact your feet receive on a daily basis. The stay-up top holds them in place even during exercise. Add these men's crew socks to your wardrobe or buy them as a gift for a loved one.
